SRMA - short read micro re-aligner 

=== To Install ===

1. Move into the c-code sub-directory.

2. Download the latest samtools from http://samtools.sf.net 
and rename the directory to 'samtools' (no quotes).

3. Run:
 sh autogen.sh && ./configure && make

=== For more help ===

see http://srma.sf.net
